divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside taking pictures and didn't notice any other than a bright light in the sky. so I tried to take a picture of it and this is how it turned out. Unfortunately this is not the first time I've taken a picture and found something really strange going on in the photo. I wanted to attribute the weirdness to a low battery or improper settings but my battery tested fine and it was set on normal nighttime setting built into the camera.
Summary: unknown light show taken with digital camera while ufo was in the area
